<div class="block-contributor">
		

		<div class="block-contributor-content">
		<div class="block-contributor-bio small">
			<p><span class="smallcaps"><strong>John Taylor Gatto</strong></span> has taught public school for twenty-six years in New York City. He&rsquo;s the author of <em>Dumbing Us Down: The Hidden Curriculum of Compulsory Schooling</em> (New Society Publishers).</p><a href="/contributors/john-taylor-gatto" class="block-contributor-link link-alt small">More From This Contributor&nbsp;&#9656;</a>		</div>
